Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,# Chant of Selflessness 無私之歌
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 副歌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.97,0:00:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}他相信道理簡單明瞭\NOne would believe in simple means
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.51,0:00:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}有人覺得也非不可能\NSome would believe it possible
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}其他人則是漠不關心\NOthers feel it won't be seen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.18,0:00:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但沒人相信會有奇蹟\NFor none believe in miracles
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.95,0:00:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}有人用鑽石換碎石\NSome give a diamond for a stone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.39,0:00:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}有人用碎石換鑽石\NSome give a stone for a diamond
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.89,0:00:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}有人守著自己的錢財\NSome keep all things for their own
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.22,0:00:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}而也有人什麼都不說\NAnd some remain in silence
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-1
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}純樸的古代，有位小女孩\NThere once lived a girl in a simpler time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.18,0:01:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}皮毛與頭髮如晝夜般\Nwith night-like hair and skin so white
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.72,0:01:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不論她到哪，都對大家說\NWherever she went, everyone she'd tell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.12,0:01:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「似是己所有，爾可當己用」\N"What'd appear as mine, 'tis thine as well"
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,## 主歌-2
